Please	 check process recovery action.<
>If you select [RESTART]					the process will restart after system initialize.<
>If you select [ABORT]					the process will be aborted.<
>If you select [JUMP]						the step that you select will be executed.<
>If you select [END]						Without Plasma Dechuck.. the process will be normally completed.<
>If you select [END_WITH_PLASMA_DECHUCK]	       With Plasma Dechuck recipe will be executed.<
>
